static final String NAME
The extension point name. This value is combined with the namespace for the extension point to form the extension point id.

PATH_ATTRIBUTE

static final String PATH_ATTRIBUTE
Name of httptransport extension point path attribute. Specifies the module path to the transport provided resources such as the loader extension JavaScript as well as any supporting resources.

This is a required attribute.
